span.p: qPCR Plate Designer — How to Use

div.style: color: rgb(17, 17, 17) !important; display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;
div.span: 1) Define Samples • Enter Name_Target_Condition • Choose Role (Control or Condition) • Set Target and Condition (auto‑parsed from name) • Pick a Color • Assign a Group • Click 'Add sample'

div.style: color: rgb(15, 36, 48) !important; display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;
div.span: 2) Design Plate A (16×24) • Select a sample color • Click wells to assign • See live legend and well counts • Use Undo/Redo or Partial reset (row or column)

div.style: color: rgb(13, 31, 26) !important; display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;
div.span: 3) Plan Master Mix • Tool auto‑counts assigned wells per Target • Enter Extra wells per Target (safety margin) • Add Reagents (µL per well) • Read per‑Target tube totals + per‑well sum

div.style: color: rgb(17, 17, 17) !important; display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;
div.span: 4) Enter Ct Values (Plate B) • Spreadsheet grid mirrors Plate A (16×24) • Paste columns or 2D blocks from Excel/Sheets • Cells stay synced with Plate A assignments

div.style: color: rgb(247, 250, 252) !important; display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;
div.span: 5) Review Analytics (Per Group) • Mean Ct per sample • ΔCt: within Target vs control type (e.g., IgG) • ΔΔCt: vs chosen control Target • Fold Change = 2^-ΔΔCt • View Ct detail table + FC bar chart

div.style: color: rgb(17, 17, 17) !important; display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;
div.span: 6) Export & Save • Export Plate A + legend (JPEG/PDF) • Export Ct Summary (all groups) (JPEG/PDF) • Export / Import full state as JSON • Hard Reset to start over

div.style: color: rgb(34, 34, 34) !important; display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
Tips
• Use Name_Target_Condition to auto‑fill fields
• Group samples (e.g., by cell line) for separate analytics
• Extra wells help account for pipetting loss
• Use Partial reset to quickly clear a row/column
• All data is saved locally (localStorage)
